# The Flash Token
Introducing $Flash token, inspired by DC Flash movie, on the BNBChain. Our objective is to create a token by the community, for the community. Unlike other tokens, our team has no assigned tokens and will purchase in the presale.

With a trading fee of 9%, we have implemented reflection mechanisms such as 3% USDT rewards, 3% liquidity automatically deposited into Pancakeswap burnt, and 3% for marketing and project development.

Our team includes experts from the DEFI world, working to bring this innovative idea of combining the hype of a DC movie with the benefits of reflection mechanisms to life.

In conclusion, $Flash token aims to bring excitement to the crypto world while benefiting our community through reflection mechanisms and expert development. Join us on this journey to the future!

